metadata.name: The Clothko #1
metadata.description:
EDITION 1 OF 1

The Clothko (/ˈkloʊθoʊ/; Greek: Κλωθώ) Collection includes 100 unique 1/1 paintings that gives tribute to Clothko a mythological God who spins the thread of human life. The thread represented human life and her decisions represented the fate of all people in society. Each work represents a unique person in the universe that Clothko created.

Artist: Godwits  
Year: 2022

Published By: Abstract Art Labs LLC  
Smart Contract Type: Manifold / ERC-721  
Artist Royalty: 10%

Limited to personal non-commercial use and resale rights of NFT are granted.
